<br>
The zone I would like to revamp, West Karana.<br>
<br>
It is a huge zone that doesn't get anymore difficult as you range further from the guards or civilization's outposts.<br>
<br>
The roads would be the safest place to travel.  Monsters would not venture into the small villages, farmers would provide food and drink to those that helped to save the farm.  In general it would no longer be a giant waste of pixels once you achieved level 11.  I know there are higher mobs, but let's face it, they are few and are not the next step up in level.<br>
<br>
Of course then it only follows that the rest of the Karanas get adjusted, since you won't need to go to them until later in your career.<br>
<br>
